ology. 0aMekeo (Papua New Guinean people)xRites and ceremonies. 0aPhilosophy, Mekeo. 0aSelf (Philosophy)xPapua New Guinea. 0aSelf (Philosophy)zPapua New Guinea. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520915275?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520915275423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520915275/original  aEBA_EMB  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles